en-US.title: Alice Street General Practice
en-US.description: Alice Street General Practice is a healthcare provider that caters to the transgender community, providing an inclusive and safe environment with services such as hormonal treatments. As a fragrance-free, informed-consent clinic, individuals from the transmasculine, transfeminine, and non-binary communities can receive quality healthcare that respects their identities and needs. This practice is also committed to education and awareness about the unique health considerations of transgender individuals.
